@Codie_Sanchez So true. 

When I interviewed hundreds of sales people, I’d ask them to pitch our product as if I was a 5 yr old

The Feynman technique is magical.

I decided to give each of @midjourney @ideogram_ai Flux and Mysic (@freepik) the same prompt to generate an image of a person.

The prompt: "A young woman with voluminous, natural curly hair stands in her bright, airy living room. She wears a vibrant wrap dress with a bold floral pattern in reds, yellows, and blues, perfectly complementing her warm skin tone. Her smile is wide and genuine, exuding confidence and approachability. Large hoop earrings and a delicate necklace add a touch of personal style. The living space around her showcases a bohemian-inspired decor with hanging plants, wooden furniture, and comfortable seating. Soft, natural light filters through nearby windows, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The color palette blends earth tones with pops of vibrant colors from the dress and decor. The overall scene captures a moment of authentic joy, emphasizing the subject's individuality and her harmonious connection to her living environment. The image should evoke a sense of cultural richness, personal comfort, and effortless style."
@midjourney @ideogram_ai @freepik A few more. @GoogleDeepMind Imagen3, @StabilityAI SD3 @Adobe Firefly and @LeonardoAi_ Phoenix https://t.co/Z7ACaslubf
@midjourney @ideogram_ai @freepik @GoogleDeepMind @StabilityAI @Adobe @LeonardoAi_ For good measure, DALL-E 3 from @ChatGPTapp https://t.co/KMObuqb5HN

